<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.10.8">
<l>eṇṇil niṉaiveyti yiṉiyillai yiṟaiyeṉṟu muṉiyāḷar tiruvār</l>
<l>paṇṇil malikīta moṭupāṭi yavarāṭa loṭukūṭa veḻilār</l>
<l>maṇṇi litupōla nakarillai yeṉavāṉa varkaḷtāma larkaḷtūy</l>
<l>naṇṇi yuṟaikiṉṟa nakarnanti puraviṇṇa karamnaṇṇu maṉamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart, go to Nantipura Viṇṇakaram, the city where celestials</l>
<l rend="indent">come and abide, scattering flowers as they say,</l>
<l>“On this vibrant earth, there is no [other] city like this,”</l>
<l>[And] as sages join together in dance, singing hymns</l>
<l rend="indent">in which flow divine tunes,</l>
<l>Attaining concentration in thought, saying, “Now there is no other god.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
